Package frc.robot.BreakerLib.util.math.functions

Interface BreakerGenericMathFunction

All Known Implementing Classes:
BreakerBezierCurve, BreakerCubic, BreakerExponential, BreakerMathFunction, BreakerMonomial, BreakerPolynomial, BreakerQuadratic
public interface BreakerGenericMathFunction
A interface for all BreakerLib classes that represent pure mathmatical functions (or equations) such as BreakerBezierCurve or BreakerQuadratic
